titleInfo.title: USA v. Morris
titleInfo.subTitle: MEMORANDUM AND ORDER as to defendant Sophia K. Morris. Due to a medical issue, defendant's appointed counsel, John Aman, cannot represent the defendant at this time. On the courts own motion, John Aman is withdrawn as counsel for the defendant, Sophia Morris. The Clerk is directed to remove Mr. Aman from all future ECF notifications in this case. Korey Reiman is hereby appointed as counsel for the defendant. Mr. Reiman shall promptly forward a copy of this memorandum and order to the defendant. Ordered by Magistrate Judge Cheryl R. Zwart. (Copy to Karen Burks) (JAB)

titleInfo.title: USA v. Morris
titleInfo.subTitle: ORDER as to defendant Sophia K. Morris. Counsel John Aman is reinstated as counsel for the defendant. Defense counsel shall confer and determine who will act as lead counsel in the case, and shall file a notice with the court stating who will be lead counsel. Lead counsel shall apprise co-counsel of any case developments until the completion of the case or until co-counsel has withdrawn from the case with leave of the court as ordered by Magistrate Judge Cheryl R. Zwart. (SED)
